‚û°Ô∏è A) Databases
‚û°Ô∏è B) Encryption Keys
‚û°Ô∏è C) Virtual Servers
Answer: B

AWS WAF can help protect applications from SQL injection attacks.
‚û°Ô∏è True / False
Answer: True

