‚û°Ô∏è True / False
Answer: True

What kind of threats does GuardDuty detect?
‚û°Ô∏è A) SQL Injection
‚û°Ô∏è B) Stolen credentials, anomalous API calls, malware
‚û°Ô∏è C) Hardware failure
Answer: B

